  "1091320": {
    "name": "殁闪像素：窥然归源",
    "steam_appid": 1091320,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": true,
    "description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1091320/extras/4362765f563e8e2517bec65afd17841d.avif?t=1768253690\" width=618 height=82 /></span><br>你在濒临崩溃的计算机系统中扮演一个像素。探索数十个色彩缤纷的世界和疯狂的文件，揭开并阻止EYE.CO的邪恶计划。发现其他像素的生活和秘密——每个人都隐藏着一些东西... <strong>你能拯救这个系统吗？</strong><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1091320/extras/7beee63442d1ae010834909e4e15e3b9.avif?t=1768253690\" width=618 height=82 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>🧭 丰富的探索！</strong></h2>DEPO为最具冒险精神的探险家提供了丰富的细节和奖励。各式各样独特的世界和文件等着你。<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>💬 充满谜团的故事！</strong></h2>系统中的每个像素都隐藏著神秘的秘密，了解它们是了解DEPO世界的关键。随著旅途的进展，他们会发生改变，并向你揭露新的讯息。解开这些谜团并不容易...<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1091320/extras/87e345384a55dcb7803742c747de1868.poster.avif?t=1768253690\" width=600 height=150 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1091320/extras/87e345384a55dcb7803742c747de1868.webm?t=1768253690\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1091320/extras/87e345384a55dcb7803742c747de1868.mp4?t=1768253690\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>👑 为场合盛装打扮</strong></h2>你可以用数十种服装来定制你的像素外观，还可以变更你自己的导弹。<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>🌐 与朋友和其他玩家线上游玩</strong></h2>与其他玩家一起完成故事模式，和他们聊天并交换物品。 <br><strong>与朋友一起玩更有趣！</strong><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1091320/extras/3eae026fc97e55ee8cfe502ac013d677.poster.avif?t=1768253690\" width=600 height=148 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1091320/extras/3eae026fc97e55ee8cfe502ac013d677.webm?t=1768253690\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1091320/extras/3eae026fc97e55ee8cfe502ac013d677.mp4?t=1768253690\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>🎮 可重玩性！</strong></h2>DEPO的后期游戏内容相当丰富，充满了新的冒险，在完成主线故事后也能享受数小时的娱乐！几乎就像一个新游戏！<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>⏱️ 竞速模式</strong></h2>DEPO中的每个文件都有竞速模式，你可以与系统中最快的像素Bill竞争。训练自己并找到数百条捷径，以令人难以置信的速度向前衝。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1091320/extras/8b2908a6741c752ff9190ad4f346728e.poster.avif?t=1768253690\" width=600 height=150 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1091320/extras/8b2908a6741c752ff9190ad4f346728e.webm?t=1768253690\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1091320/extras/8b2908a6741c752ff9190ad4f346728e.mp4?t=1768253690\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>⚽ 多人迷你游戏</strong></h2>如果故事模式还不够，还有5个令人兴奋的多人迷你游戏，在这里你的友谊将受到严峻考验...<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>🛠️ 关卡编辑器</strong></h2>你还可以创建自己的关卡并与社群分享。尽情发挥你的创造力。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1091320/extras/3bb0c9b35abc343bcfa9a62e88682e1d.poster.avif?t=1768253690\" width=600 height=150 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1091320/extras/3bb0c9b35abc343bcfa9a62e88682e1d.webm?t=1768253690\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1091320/extras/3bb0c9b35abc343bcfa9a62e88682e1d.mp4?t=1768253690\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>点击右侧的社交媒体图标，加入DEPO Discord社群 👉🏼 👉🏼</strong><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1091320/extras/298b85644618eea74770be2b539fb9a2.avif?t=1768253690\" width=569 height=82 /></span>",
